<%# Head / Meta Data %>
<% title("The SimpliFly Team") %>
<% meta_description("Meet the experienced team of instructors at Simplifly in Mesa, Phoenix, Scottsdale, and Spanish Fork, Salt Lake. Our knowledgeable and dedicated instructors are committed to your pilot training success. Many of our students come from Gilbert, Chandler, Tempe, Scottsdale, Apache Junction, Queen Creek, Fountain Hills, Gold Canyon, Maricopa, Pinal, Springville, Provo, Payson, Mapleton, Salem, Elk Ridge, Utah County, Juab County") %>
